attributes.name: Denver Streets Partnership
attributes.description: The Denver Streets Partnership coalition advocates for people-friendly streets, so that walking, biking, scooting, and transit can be the first choices of transportation. Together, we advocate for better sidewalk, bike lane and transit funding, policies, and street design.
